{
  "stem": "5799.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If I ate your potato, I lived longer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In a army, if I shared my potato with you, we both live longer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You die one for another.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it's-- I am proud that I was a partisan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My horse gave her life for me, my [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Galla. ?] Her name was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Galla. ?] The last day we had an order that the Nazis are running through the woods not to let them through.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know, I wasn't the leader.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, they give you-- if you had a little education, they made a lieutenant out of you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You were an officer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If you knew how to write, you were an officer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this was a hill, and we were 10 guys with one girl, and in the middle was a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were running towards us, and everybody was dead and I was in the middle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was shooting and shooting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The last face I will remember till the day I die, that was a face of a Nazi not much more-- not, not much older than I-- must have been 19, with the blonde hair, running.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then I saw blood, means I killed him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was shooting and I was shooting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in that minute, my horse came running from this little stable I had and covered me with her body, and got a bullet in her belly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Galla was-- horses, when they die, they cry, just like [INAUDIBLE] now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I can cry after a horse, I'm still human, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was dying, and I cannot shoot her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A bullet in the stomach, forget it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You cannot operate on a horse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband was told that this hill-- next day, you are going to the city already.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
